data.mission: Consolidate and synthesize recent cognitive work, research findings, and insights into a comprehensive knowledge report. Review accumulated thoughts, agent findings, and memory patterns to identify key themes, connections, and knowledge gaps.

Investigate the unresolved/missing mathematical objective by analyzing the current state, identifying gaps or ambiguities, and proposing a minimal set of mathematically rigorous steps to resolve the issue. Produce a prioritized plan (definitions, lemmas, calculations, or experiments) that closes the gap and specifies any additional data or tools required.
